snippet.title: A Voice For Survivors 2021 Project
snippet.description:
A channel dedicated in addressing #AmberHeard directly as a survivor of abuse. Each video will be a dedicated direct letter to a number of people within the inner Heard circle, as well as to show our support to other survivors who want the world to know #AmberHeardDoesNotSpeakForUs.

The world has become a sad place for survivors in the wake of the UK ruling against #JohnnyDepp and thankfully a new retrial has been ordered and there may eventually be #JusticeForJohnnyDepp #JusticeForSurvivors and #JusticeForTheAbused. 

First video will be posted before 1st January 2021. Please like and subscribe so you don't miss the first of many videos.
